{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Revert back to using the title of His Majesty\u2019s Government and not UK Government",
        "additional_details": "I believe that is a disgrace, it is a break with our history and our traditions and I want Parliament to ensure that it remain His Majesty\u2019s government.\r\n\r\nParliament must block His Majesty\u2019s government from changing its name to UK government. It must not be allowed to happen. They must revert back to the old saying of His Majesty\u2019s government. I think it is a disgrace that this government is breaking our tradition.",
        "background": "His Majesty\u2019s government have decided to use 'UK Government' as the primary identity for all public-facing communications. Instead of it being his Majesty\u2019s government, it is now UK Government. ",
